\id 2JN - Maiwa NT [mti] -Papua New Guinea 2011 (web version -2017) 
\h 2 Jon 
\toc1 Jon Gigirum Meuma Duwameba 
\toc2 2 Jon 
\toc3 2Jn 
\mt1 2 JON  
\mt2 Jon Gigirum Meuma Duwameba  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Siosi amaraivi abnawa gumbe aig vesin me God wagomiyanewa ge usitainawa gumbo. Baigan neuma undag ye guniyap. Ne nekut onan, natawa anoyawa undag baigan ye guniyap.  
\v 2 Me natawa me nu danunup wakeiviwa gumbe. Me nu danunup yaibobot wakeigimpe.   
\p
\v 3 Ne anoeniwa, ano oraiwa, ano nunigimtan ge yum nu Mamunwa God, ge Iesu Keriso Mamunwa Usiwa me gumbe uwag nu gunup wakeigimpe natawa ge baigan danave.   
\p
\v 4 \x + \xo 1:4 \xt 3Jn 3\x*Ne degadega kokavit ana, kuiyawa ne anona ud geuma upeba nu Mamunwa Gwangwan wag didnunne me mina natawa gumbe wakeg amome.  
\v 5 \x + \xo 1:5 \xt 1Jn 2:7\x*Ge vesin oraiwa. Gare ne wag dirukna. Ne gwangwan mataiwa den teeni. Me amatonewa apa autuwa. Nu baigan garagara ata.  
\v 6 Baigan me nu gwangwan gumbe vin anigimtanwa, sira gwangwan me baigan gumbe vin anigimtanwa, me anoyana amatonewa apa.   
\p
\v 7 \x + \xo 1:7 \xt 1Jn 4:1-3\x*Ama toreya igiyawa obiren dauwag piyu mame gumbe uwaya. Mu taibe den waya Iesu Keriso me kwapiven ag uwane. Apan meiba me ama toreya abnawa sira me Keriso anaviyawa.  
\v 8 Ye amat yaimoyai aya. Garawa me oya nu nau etewa me den waropiyaya, sira garawa yeuma matai undag enwabot auya.  
\v 9 Apan da Iesu Keriso toyau toyau meuma gumbe utunut aine, sira den wakenewa, me God gaibu onan. Toyau toyau meuma gumbe wakenewa me Mamawa ge Usiwa maun gumbo yumnasivi.  
\v 10 Meoya apan da toyau toyau mame guniyap den aug uwapewa gwe yeuma den unikpe, sira kaiwa kaiwa gumbe den waya.  
\v 11 Apan da me apan meiba kaiwa kaiwa wapewa, me matai anoano kukaeba meuma waita wampe gaibu ampe.   
\p
\v 12 Ne ye guniyap gae obiren tetan anoeni, go ne anoeniwa pepa\f + \fr 1:12 \ft Me en mina. \f* ge ink\f + \fr 1:12 \ft Me kapupun sira yoi mina.\f* gumbe den tetna. Ne anoeniwa yenan amdau onetna garayau aka gae ye gaibu watna. Me gumbe degadega numa noidauwape.   
\p
\v 13 Yogiyagwa wagomiyanewa me usitainawa mu ge gungap kaiwa kaiwa barauya.   